# desktop role — base graphical workstation layer.
# Composes the AwesomeWM desktop, full audio, Bluetooth, SSH access,
# and common CLI tools. Pair with devbox (Liquorix kernel) or macbook
# (T2 hardware) as the kernel/hardware base:
#
#   ./build.sh --profile "devbox desktop" --host mymachine
#   ./build.sh --profile "macbook desktop" --host mymachine
awesomewm
audio-pipewire
bluetooth
dev-tools
ssh-server
wifi
